In `run.js` line ~145, you calculate usage via `contextTokens = totalUsage.input_tokens + totalUsage.output_tokens`. Because the agent submits the *entire cumulative transcript* back to the model on every generation cycle, `input_tokens` actually represents the sum of all historical tokens, not the size of the current context window.
