jq -s 'map(select(.type == "runner_model_request_built")) | last | .payload.system' /tmp/runner_trace.jsonl

# If you see "ttl" anywhere under cache_control, that flag violates the live API schema.
```

To see the *actual* upstream wiring, you could temporarily intercept locally (runner-side) in `modelClient` or add a local bridge debug endpoint (`/v1/debug`) that emits the current credential mode.

